pl.bristleback.server.bristle.serialization.system

Class PropertySerialization

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.bristleback.server.bristle.serialization.system.PropertySerialization

  • public class PropertySerialization
extends Object
    Objects of this class contains meta information about single serialization operation definition. Serialization operation may come from server/client action resolvers or just from ConditionObjectSender. Used by system serialization engines, like JsonSerializationEngine.

    Created on: 2011-09-04 16:36:29

    Author:
    Wojciech Niemiec
